    "title": "Vacancy for Category Manager at Goibibo Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Category Manager looking for your next big career move? Goibibo Advisory Limited in Varanasi offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Goibibo Advisory Limited:\nGoibibo Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Goibibo Advisory Limited!",
